  "texts": [
    "In the first stage, TIP identifies nonsensical concepts within the nonsensical statement, and in the second stage, it incorporates implicit knowledge to construct prompts that enable LLMs to generate more accurate explanations.",
    "• We conduct experiments on two commonsense explanation generation datasets, including a new dataset that we constructed semiautomatically.",
    "The results across various LLMs consistently demonstrate the effectiveness of our proposed framework on all metrics.• We analyze the experimental results and demonstrate the generality of our approach, showcasing that our proposed method effectively enhances the LLMs' commonsense reasoning ability.The rest of this paper is organized as follows.",
    "In Sect. 2, we review works that are highly relevant to commonsense explanation generation.",
    "In Sect. 3, we provide a detailed explanation of the proposed framework TIP."
